                 <div class="text-[.68rem] text-[var(--text-muted)]">${PROFILE_I18N.weekPending}</div>`
              : `<div class="text-[.75rem] text-amber-600">${PROFILE_I18N.weekChooseTribe}</div>`}
          </a>

          <a href="/gamification" class="bg-emerald-50/60 rounded-xl p-3 no-underline block hover:ring-1 hover:ring-emerald-200 transition-all">
